sources.description:
Street Racers Take Down Drug Kingpin | Fast Atlanta | Action Thriller Movie - In Atlanta, a team of street racers puts their skills to the test when they discover a local drug dealer is preying on vulnerable women. Racing through the city streets, dodging the law, and using every trick in their arsenal, they work together to bring the criminal down. As the stakes rise and danger closes in, their loyalty, speed, and courage are pushed to the limit in a high-octane fight for justice.

2024.  Stars: Jason Park, Ashanti Harris, Brandon Dunlap
